data.name: Conkley's Finobe Darker Theme
data.description: For those who want a darker finobe theme, here you go. For any feedback message me on the finobe site. Make sure you use Finobe's default dark theme of course (otherwise many elements will render incorrectly).

data.name: 2b2t.io Customizable Theme (Default: Dark)
data.description: I recommend using the Stylus browser extension. This is a simple customizable theme for 2b2t.io The default configuration is dark but it is fully configurable. If you like the look of any of the examples images their configurations are as follows: Text : FFFFFF Total: F5A623 Que: 006CFF Prio: FF0000 (Grey) Background: 414141 (Red) Background: 800000 (Green) Background: 008000 (Blue) Background: 000080
